1. *Brine* se o svojoj budućnosti. (He worries about his future.)
2. On je *brinuo* o svojoj porodici. (He was taking care of his family.)
3. *Brižno* je brinuo o svom zdravlju. (He was taking care of his health carefully.)
4. Svi su *brinuli* o starijima. (Everyone was taking care of the elderly.)
5. Ona je *brinula* o svojoj deci. (She was taking care of her children.)
6. Deca su *brinula* o zdravlju svojih roditelja. (The children were taking care of their parents' health.)